##Spring on our doorstep

WECHAT denganqing1984

Features, here, I will share my writing, reading the book.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Five years ago I wrote this:

"I was a little excited when I heard the sound of rain in my sleep yesterday. I haven't heard it for a long time. It's so hard to imagine a rain in Beijing in such dry weather day after day.

Wake up in the middle of the night, like a child afraid to like the people while they sleep quietly away, the rain is still, and then sleep peacefully.

Early in the morning, went to the yard, the road has a small puddle, Forsythia also withered some, the air is moist. It's kind of like home in the south."
Almost every year, I have this feeling of homesickness. Beijing as long as a rare rain, I have the illusion of returning home.

The leaves of the Ash tree, washed clean by the rain, glowed green; the February orchids below the crabapple in Xifu, blossoming purple-blue petals in clusters; the mountain tops on the outskirts of Beijing, a fluffy peach blossom on the dry ground..

All this makes me sad. The Spring in Beijing is still rather dry. And the south that ubiquitous moisture, can only be retained in the memory.

Unexpectedly, this year I will usher in a spring in my hometown in the south. After several spring rains, rape flowers were in full bloom in front and behind the house. Sitting in the room reading, the wind from the window up, fragrant flowers.

Gray clouds in the morning still covered the sky, to the afternoon exposed the blue sky. In the fields, Veronica, cardamine, Sonchus OLERACEA, also opened a small flower.

In the far field, my aunt and uncle were busy digging up the soil with a spade. Every family drying up the quilt, after all, is in the river, a few days do not sun, bedding are wet. We sat in the sun, ate sunflower seeds, peeled peanuts, and the dog chased its tail.
This is the first spring I've spent in my hometown in more than a decade. Every year back home, almost all the wind and rain, cold winter, gloomy sky, everywhere wet cold.

After a few days, I was eager to return to Beijing, after all, the heated room is more comfortable, even if I do not see the spring scenery I want.
Now it's a blessing in disguise because the epidemic has been at home for so long. I don't know when I will be able to return to Beijing, but I seem to have the idea of "staying at home is also good" in my mind.

In any case, Spring Day is changing every day, everything is growing, spring water ripples, let a person's heart surging with hope. I don't want to miss a minute.

Just after a spring rain

Clouds float in the sky in front of the House

The wind blew away the clouds and sent the fragrance of flowers.

All kinds of little flowers are blooming on our doorstep.
